"literal>, for example:"
msgstr ""
"如果您希望默认启用此功能，则需要通过添加 <literal>config.elemental.reset."
"enabled: true</literal>，来确保 <literal>MachineRegistration</literal> 明确启"
"用此功能，例如："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:335
msgid ""
