#: l10n/source/edge.xml:818
msgid "Installing Open-iSCSI"
msgstr "安装 Open-iSCSI"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:819
msgid ""
"A core requirement of deploying and using Longhorn is the installation of "
"the <literal>open-iscsi</literal> package and the <literal>iscsid</literal> "
"daemon running on all Kubernetes nodes.  This is necessary, since Longhorn "
"relies on <literal>iscsiadm</literal> on the host to provide persistent "
"volumes to Kubernetes."
msgstr ""
"要部署并使用 Longhorn，需满足的一项核心要求是安装 <literal>open-iscsi</"
"literal> 软件包并在所有 Kubernetes 节点上运行 <literal>iscsid</literal> 守护"
"程序。之所以有此要求，是因为 Longhorn 依赖于主机上的 <literal>iscsiadm</"
"literal> 来为 Kubernetes 提供永久卷。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:820
msgid "Let’s install it:"
msgstr "我们来安装此软件包："

