"确定要为特定用例使用哪些 <literal>Day 2</literal> 资源（<xref linkend=\"day2-"
"determine-use-case\"/>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1757
msgid ""
"The suggested workflow sequence (<xref linkend=\"day2-upgrade-workflow\"/>) "
