"如果您的用例需要使用 Fleet（<xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>）但不使用 "
"Rancher，可以完全跳过 Rancher 组件的设置。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1762
msgid ""
"Responsible for the management of your <literal>downstream clusters</"
"literal>. Should be deployed on your <literal>management cluster</literal>."
