#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1767
msgid ""
"For more information on installing Fleet as a standalone component, see "
"Fleet’s <link xl:href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/installation\">Installation "
"Details</link>."
msgstr ""
"有关将 Fleet 安装为独立组件的详细信息，请参见 Fleet 的<link xl:"
"href=\"https://fleet.rancher.io/installation\">安装细节</link>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1768
msgid ""
"For more information regarding the Fleet component, see <xref "
"linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>."
msgstr ""
"有关 Fleet 组件的详细信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"components-fleet\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><important><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1769
msgid ""
"This documentation heavily relies on <literal>Fleet</literal> and more "
"specifically on the <literal>GitRepo</literal> and <literal>Bundle</literal> "
"resources (more on this in <xref linkend=\"day2-determine-use-case\"/>) for "
"establishing a GitOps way of automating the deployment of resources related "
"to <literal>Day 2</literal> operations."
msgstr ""
"本文档主要依赖于 <literal>Fleet</literal>，更具体地说，依赖于使用 "
"<literal>GitRepo</literal> 和<literal>捆绑包</literal>资源（有关详细信息，请"
"参见<xref linkend=\"day2-determine-use-case\"/>）来通过 GitOps 自动部署与 "
