"role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 如何在群集<emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>"
"工作</emphasis></emphasis>节点上进行操作系统升级。如果群集仅由<emphasis>控制"
"平面</emphasis>节点组成，则<emphasis role=\"strong\">不会</emphasis>对其进行"
"解释。它会在所有控制平面 <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 计划成功完"
"成后执行。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1846
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Control Plane SUC Plan</emphasis> - instructs "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> on how to do an OS upgrade on "
"cluster <emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>control-plane</emphasis></"
"emphasis> nodes."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">控制平面 SUC 计划</emphasis> - 告知 <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 如何在群集<emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>"
"控制平面</emphasis></emphasis>节点上执行操作系统升级。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1847
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Script Secret</emphasis> - referenced in each "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plan</emphasis>; ships an <literal>upgrade.sh</"
"literal> script responsible for creating the <literal>os-pkg-update.service/"
"os-migration.service</literal> which will do the actual OS upgrade."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">脚本密钥</emphasis> - 在每个 <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>中引用；提供负责创建 <literal>os-pkg-"
"update.service/os-migration.service</literal>（执行实际的操作系统升级）的 "
"<literal>upgrade.sh</literal> 脚本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1848
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Script Data ConfigMap</emphasis> - referenced in "
"each <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plan</emphasis>; ships configurations "
"used by the <literal>upgrade.sh</literal> script."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">脚本数据 ConfigMap</emphasis> - 在每个 <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>中引用；提供 <literal>upgrade.sh</"
"literal> 脚本使用的配置。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><note><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1849
msgid ""
"The above resources will be deployed in the <literal>cattle-system</literal> "
"namespace of each downstream cluster."
msgstr ""
"上述资源将部署在每个下游群集的 <literal>cattle-system</literal> 名称空间中。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1850 l10n/source/edge.xml:1978
msgid ""
"On the downstream cluster, <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> picks up "
"the newly deployed <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plans</emphasis> and "
"deploys an <emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>Update Pod</emphasis></"
"emphasis> on each node that matches the <emphasis role=\"strong\">node "
"selector</emphasis> defined in the <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC Plan</"
"emphasis>. For information how to monitor the <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC "
"Plan Pod</emphasis>, refer to <xref linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-"
"controller-monitor-plans\"/>."
msgstr ""
"在下游群集上，<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC</emphasis> 将拾取新部署的 "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>，并在与 <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">SUC 计划</emphasis>中定义的<emphasis role=\"strong\">节点选择"
"器</emphasis>匹配的每个节点上部署<emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>更新 "
"Pod</emphasis></emphasis>。有关如何监控 <emphasis role=\"strong\">SUC 计划 "
"Pod</emphasis> 的信息，请参见<xref linkend=\"components-system-upgrade-"
"controller-monitor-plans\"/>。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1851
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Update Pod</emphasis> (deployed on each node) "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">mounts</emphasis> the script Secret and <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">executes</emphasis> the <literal>upgrade.sh</literal> script "
"that the Secret ships."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">更新 Pod</emphasis>（部署在每个节点上）<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">会挂载</emphasis>脚本密钥并<emphasis role=\"strong\">执行</"
"emphasis>密钥附带的 <literal>upgrade.sh</literal> 脚本。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1852
msgid "The <literal>upgrade.sh</literal> proceeds to do the following:"
msgstr "<literal>upgrade.sh</literal> 继续执行以下操作："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1853
msgid ""
"Based on its configurations, determine whether the OS needs a package "
"update, or it needs to be migrated."
msgstr "根据其配置，确定操作系统是需要更新软件包，还是需要迁移。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1854
msgid ""
"Based on the above outcome it will create either a <literal>os-pkg-update."
"service</literal> (for package updates), or a <literal>os-migration.service</"
"literal> (for migration). The service will be of type <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">oneshot</emphasis> and will adopt the following workflow:"
msgstr ""
"基于上述结果，它将创建一个 <literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal>（用于软件"
"包更新）或 <literal>os-migration.service</literal>（用于迁移）。该服务将为 "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">oneshot</emphasis> 类型，并将采用以下工作流程："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1855
msgid "For <literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal>:"
msgstr "对于<literal>os-pkg-update.service</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1856
msgid ""
"Update all package versions on the node OS, by running "
"<literal>transactional-update cleanup up</literal>"
msgstr ""
"通过运行 <literal>transactional-update cleanup up</literal> 更新节点操作系统"
"上的所有软件包版本"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1857
msgid ""
"After a successful <literal>transactional-update</literal>, schedule a "
"system <emphasis role=\"strong\">reboot</emphasis> so that the package "
"version updates can take effect"
msgstr ""
"成功执行 <literal>transactional-update</literal> 后，将安排系统<emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">重引导</emphasis>，使软件包版本更新生效"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1858
msgid "For <literal>os-migration.service</literal>:"
msgstr "对于 <literal>os-migration.service</literal>："

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1859
msgid ""
"Update all package versions on the node OS, by running "
"<literal>transactional-update cleanup up</literal>. This is done to ensure "
"that no old package versions cause an OS migration error."
msgstr ""
"通过运行 <literal>transactional-update cleanup up</literal> 来更新节点操作系"
"统上的所有软件包版本。这样做是为了确保不会因为软件包版本较旧而导致操作系统迁"
"移错误。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1860
msgid ""
"Proceed to migrate the OS to the desired values. Migration is done by "
"utilizing the <literal>zypper migration</literal> command."
msgstr ""
"继续将操作系统迁移到所需值。迁移通过使用 <literal>zypper migration</literal> "
"命令完成。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1861
msgid ""
"Schedule a system <emphasis role=\"strong\">reboot</emphasis> so that the "
"migration can take effect"
msgstr "安排系统<emphasis role=\"strong\">重引导</emphasis>，以便迁移生效"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1862
msgid ""
"Start the <literal>os-pkg-update.service/os-migration.service</literal> and "
"wait for it to complete."
msgstr ""
"启动 <literal>os-pkg-update.service/os-migration.service</literal> 并等待其完"
"成。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1863
msgid ""
"Cleanup the <literal>os-pkg-update.service/os-migration.service</literal> "
"after the <emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>systemd.service</emphasis></"
"emphasis> has done its job. It is removed from the system to ensure that no "
"accidental executions/reboots happen in the future."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>systemd.service</emphasis></emphasis> 完"
"成其工作后会将 <literal>os-pkg-update.service/os-migration.service</literal> "
"从系统中去除，以确保将来不会发生意外的执行/重引导。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:1864
msgid ""
"The OS upgrade procedure finishes with the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\"><emphasis>system reboot</emphasis></emphasis>. After the "
"reboot, the OS package versions are upgraded and if the Edge release "
"requires it, the OS might be migrated as well."
msgstr ""
"操作系统升级过程会在<emphasis role=\"strong\"><emphasis>系统重引导</"
"emphasis></emphasis>后完成。重引导后，操作系统软件包版本将升级，操作系统还可"
"能根据 Edge 版本的要求进行迁移。"

