"upgrade his chart(s) to."
msgstr ""
"该工作流程的第一个步骤是用户<link xl:href=\"https://helm.sh/docs/helm/"
"helm_pull/\">提取</link>其 chart 要升级到的新 Helm chart 存档。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><section><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:2174
msgid ""
"The archive(s) should then be placed in a directory that will be processed "
"by the <literal>generate-chart-upgrade-data.sh</literal> script."
msgstr ""
