"<literal>v1.30.11+rke2r1</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"<literal>${RKE2_VERSION}</literal> 是要使用的 <literal>RKE2</literal> 版本，"
"请替换此值（例如替换为 <literal>v1.30.5+rke2r1</literal>）。"

#. type: Content of: <book><part><chapter><section><para>
#: l10n/source/edge.xml:3079 l10n/source/edge.xml:3086
